Editing the sprint field to have a random string will produce a NumberFormatException
Editing the sprint field to have a number that isn't the id of a sprint will produce a NullPointerException

This affects Bonfire as users would expect the field to accept values.

When loading the JIRA 5.1 bugfix rapidboard with the following URL: https://jdog.atlassian.net/secure/RapidBoard.jspa?rapidView=171&view=detail&selectedIssue=JRADEV-12429&quickFilter=488

