Exception: Uncaught TypeError: Object [object Object] has no method 'fancybox'
Resource: https://jdog.atlassian.net/s/en_US8i94yk/763/938/a00eeabd6855fb35f7a8e53a714f09ed/_/download/contextbatch/js/gh-rapid/batch.js
